<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>CHEAP — CLI Code Editor</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    /* ─── Reset & Base ─── */
    *, *::before, *::after {
      margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: #0B0806;
      color: #FFF1E8;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }
    ul { list-style: none; }

    /* ─── Utility ─── */
    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }

    /* ─── Noise Overlay ─── */
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 9999;
      pointer-events: none;
      opacity: 0.035;
      background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
      background-size: 256px 256px;
    }

    /* ─── Navbar ─── */
    .navbar {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      padding: 16px 0;
      background: rgba(11, 8, 6, 0.7);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 241, 232, 0.06);
    }
    .navbar .container {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .nav-logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      color: #FFF1E8;
    }
    .nav-logo span {
      color: #D48148;
    }
    .nav-logo .logo-bracket {
      color: #5C4A3C;
    }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .nav-links a {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #A89F98;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: #FFF1E8;
    }
    .nav-cta {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D48148, #b86a3a);
      color: #FFF1E8 !important;
      padding: 10px 22px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600 !important;
      font-size: 0.85rem !important;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(212, 129, 72, 0.3);
    }

    /* ─── Hero ─── */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding-top: 80px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-bg-glow {
      position: absolute;
      top: -200px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 800px;
      height: 800px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(212,129,72,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero .container {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .hero-left {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      background: rgba(212, 129, 72, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 129, 72, 0.2);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #f0a070;
      width: fit-content;
    }
    .hero-badge-dot {
      width: 6px; height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #22c55e;
      animation: pulse-dot 2s infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse-dot {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
      50% { opacity: 0.4; }
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 3.8rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }
    .hero h1 .gradient-text {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF1E8 0%, #f0a070 50%, #D48148 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #A89F98;
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 480px;
    }
    .hero-ctas {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D48148, #b86a3a);
      color: #FFF1E8;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(212, 129, 72, 0.35);
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: transparent;
      color: #FFF1E8;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 241, 232, 0.12);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 241, 232, 0.05);
      border-color: rgba(255, 241, 232, 0.2);
    }
    .hero-stats {
      display: flex;
      gap: 32px;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .hero-stat h3 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #FFF1E8;
    }
    .hero-stat h3 span { color: #D48148; }
    .hero-stat p {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #6B5E55;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    /* ─── Terminal Mockup ─── */
    .terminal-mock {
      position: relative;
    }
    .terminal-window {
      background: #050302;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 241, 232, 0.08);
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.6), 0 0 0 1px rgba(212,129,72,0.05);
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }
    .terminal-window:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }
    .terminal-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 241, 232, 0.03);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 241, 232, 0.06);
    }
    .terminal-dot {
      width: 10px; height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }
    .terminal-dot.red { background: #ff5f56; }
    .terminal-dot.yellow { background: #ffbd2e; }
    .terminal-dot.green { background: #27c93f; }
    .terminal-title {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: #5C4A3C;
      margin-left: 8px;
    }
    .terminal-body {
      padding: 24px;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #c4b5a5;
      min-height: 320px;
    }
    .terminal-line {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeLine 0.4s forwards;
    }
    .terminal-line:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
    .terminal-line:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
    .terminal-line:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1.6s; }
    .terminal-line:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 2.6s; }
    .terminal-line:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 3.4s; }
    .terminal-line:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 4.2s; }
    .terminal-line:nth-child(7) { animation-delay: 5.0s; }
    @keyframes fadeLine {
      to { opacity: 1; }
    }
    .terminal-prompt {
      color: #D48148;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .terminal-cmd {
      color: #FFF1E8;
    }
    .terminal-output {
      color: #6B5E55;
      padding-left: 28px;
    }
    .terminal-output.success {
      color: #4ade80;
    }
    .terminal-output.info {
      color: #60a5fa;
    }
    .terminal-output.warning {
      color: #fbbf24;
    }
    .terminal-cursor {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 8px;
      height: 16px;
      background: #D48148;
      animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
      vertical-align: text-bottom;
      margin-left: 4px;
    }
    @keyframes blink {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
      50% { opacity: 0; }
    }
    .terminal-chevron {
      color: #5C4A3C;
    }
    .terminal-glowing-border {
      position: absolute;
      inset: -2px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(212,129,72,0.2), transparent, rgba(212,129,72,0.1));
      z-index: -1;
      opacity: 0.5;
    }

    /* ─── Features Section ─── */
    .features {
      padding: 100px 0;
      position: relative;
    }
    .section-label {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #D48148;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .section-sub {
      color: #A89F98;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      max-width: 500px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 50px;
    }
    .feature-card {
      background: rgba(24, 17, 12, 0.6);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 241, 232, 0.06);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 32px;
      transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
    }
    .feature-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(212, 129, 72, 0.2);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }
    .feature-card.feature-wide {
      grid-column: span 1;
    }
    .feature-card.feature-tall {
      grid-row: span 1;
    }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 44px; height: 44px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      background: rgba(212, 129, 72, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 129, 72, 0.15);
    }
    .feature-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .feature-card p {
      color: #A89F98;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .feature-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 14px;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      background: rgba(212, 129, 72, 0.08);
      color: #f0a070;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 129, 72, 0.1);
    }

    /* ─── Workflow Section ─── */
    .workflow {
      padding: 80px 0;
    }
    .workflow .container {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .workflow-commands {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .workflow-command {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      background: rgba(24, 17, 12, 0.4);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 241, 232, 0.05);
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .workflow-command:hover {
      background: rgba(24, 17, 12, 0.8);
      border-color: rgba(212, 129, 72, 0.2);
    }
    .workflow-cmd-icon {
      width: 32px; height: 32px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: rgba(212, 129, 72, 0.1);
      color: #D48148;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .workflow-cmd-text {
      color: #FFF1E8;
      flex: 1;
    }
    .workflow-cmd-arrow {
      color: #5C4A3C;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
    .workflow-right {
      position: relative;
    }
    .code-block {
      background: #050302;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 241, 232, 0.06);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: #c4b5a5;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .code-line {
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .code-comment { color: #5C4A3C; }
    .code-keyword { color: #f0a070; }
    .code-string { color: #4ade80; }
    .code-func { color: #60a5fa; }
    .code-var { color: #fbbf24; }

    /* ─── Footer ─── */
    .footer {
      padding: 40px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 241, 232, 0.06);
    }
    .footer .container {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .footer-left {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #5C4A3C;
    }
    .footer-left span { color: #D48148; }
    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .footer-links a {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #6B5E55;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .footer-links a:hover {
      color: #A89F98;
    }

    /* ─── Responsive ─── */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .hero h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; }
      .hero .container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
      .hero-right { order: -1; }
      .terminal-body { min-height: 240px; }
      .section-title { font-size: 2rem; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
      .hero p { font-size: 1rem; }
      .hero-stats { gap: 20px; }
      .hero-stat h3 { font-size: 1.4rem; }
      .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .workflow .container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .footer .container { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- ─── Navbar ─── -->
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="nav-logo">
        <span class="logo-bracket">~</span>
        cheap<span>@</span>cli
        <span class="logo-bracket">$</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
        <li><a href="#workflow">Workflow</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Docs</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">GitHub</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" class="nav-cta">Install →</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ─── Hero ─── -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg-glow"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-left">
        <div class="hero-badge">
          <span class="hero-badge-dot"></span>
          v2.4.1 — AI-powered CLI
        </div>
        <h1>
          Code at the<br/>
          <span class="gradient-text">Speed of Thought</span>
        </h1>
        <p>
          An intelligent, autonomous CLI code editor that understands your project,
          writes production-ready code, and never leaves your terminal.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-ctas">
          <button class="btn-primary" onclick="alert('🍺 Cheers! Install via: curl -fsSL https://cheap.sh | sh')">
            <span>⌘</span> Install Now
          </button>
          <button class="btn-secondary" onclick="document.getElementById('features').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">
            See Features →
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stats">
          <div class="hero-stat">
            <h3>14<span>k</span></h3>
            <p>GitHub Stars</p>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-stat">
            <h3>2.4<span>k</span></h3>
            <p>Daily Users</p>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-stat">
            <h3>99<span>%</span></h3>
            <p>Uptime</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-right">
        <div class="terminal-mock">
          <div class="terminal-glowing-border"></div>
          <div class="terminal-window">
            <div class="terminal-header">
              <span class="terminal-dot red"></span>
              <span class="terminal-dot yellow"></span>
              <span class="terminal-dot green"></span>
              <span class="terminal-title">cheap — ~/project (zsh)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="terminal-body">
              <div class="terminal-line">
                <span class="terminal-prompt">❯</span>
                <span class="terminal-cmd">cheap "create a landing page with React"</span>
              </div>
              <div class="terminal-line">
                <span class="terminal-output info">⊙ Analyzing project structure...</span>
              </div>
              <div class="terminal-line">
                <span class="terminal-output success">✔ Generated Landing.jsx</span>
              </div>
              <div class="terminal-line">
                <span class="terminal-output success">✔ Generated Landing.css</span>
              </div>
              <div class="terminal-line">
                <span class="terminal-output info">⊙ Installing dependencies...</span>
              </div>
              <div class="terminal-line">
                <span class="terminal-output warning">⚠ Minor lint warnings — auto-fixing...</span>
              </div>
              <div class="terminal-line">
                <span class="terminal-prompt">❯</span>
                <span class="terminal-cmd">cheap "add dark mode toggle"</span>
                <span class="terminal-cursor"></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Features Section ─── -->
  <section class="features" id="features">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">✦ Features</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Built for the Terminal.<br/>Powered by AI.</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">
        Everything you need to build, debug, and ship — without leaving your command line.
      </p>

      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🧠</div>
          <h3>Autonomous Code Gen</h3>
          <p>Describe what you want in plain English. CHEAP writes complete, production-ready files with zero hand-holding.</p>
          <span class="feature-tag">multi-file</span>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🔧</div>
          <h3>Self-Healing Mode</h3>
          <p>Detects lint errors, broken imports, and type mismatches — then fixes them automatically before you even notice.</p>
          <span class="feature-tag">auto-fix</span>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🌐</div>
          <h3>Web-Aware Search</h3>
          <p>When you hit an unknown API or package, CHEAP searches the web, reads docs, and generates the integration code.</p>
          <span class="feature-tag">web-search</span>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">📎</div>
          <h3>Context Engine</h3>
          <p>Analyzes your entire project — file tree, imports, configs — so every generated line fits perfectly into your codebase.</p>
          <span class="feature-tag">full-context</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Workflow Section ─── -->
  <section class="workflow" id="workflow">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="workflow-left">
        <div class="section-label">⚡ Workflow</div>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="font-size:2.2rem;">Your New<br/>Development Loop</h2>
        <p class="section-sub" style="margin-bottom:30px;">
          No more context-switching between browser, editor, and terminal. Everything happens in one place.
        </p>
        <div class="workflow-commands">
          <div class="workflow-command">
            <span class="workflow-cmd-icon">→</span>
            <span class="workflow-cmd-text"><span style="color:#D48148;">cheap</span> "build a todo app with React"</span>
            <span class="workflow-cmd-arrow">⌘⏎</span>
          </div>
          <div class="workflow-command">
            <span class="workflow-cmd-icon">→</span>
            <span class="workflow-cmd-text"><span style="color:#D48148;">cheap</span> "add a dark mode toggle"</span>
            <span class="workflow-cmd-arrow">⌘⏎</span>
          </div>
          <div class="workflow-command">
            <span class="workflow-cmd-icon">→</span>
            <span class="workflow-cmd-text"><span style="color:#D48148;">cheap</span> "fix the login form validation"</span>
            <span class="workflow-cmd-arrow">⌘⏎</span>
          </div>
          <div class="workflow-command">
            <span class="workflow-cmd-icon">→</span>
            <span class="workflow-cmd-text"><span style="color:#D48148;">cheap</span> "search web for stripe webhook docs"</span>
            <span class="workflow-cmd-arrow">⌘⏎</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="workflow-right">
        <div class="code-block">
